+General Component Design Rules
+
+Keep components small and focused - if they exceed 100 lines, break them down.
+Give each component a single clear responsibility.
+Extract commonly used UI elements into reusable components.
+Keep state management close to where the state is used.
+Maintain clear separation between UI and business logic.


